# Media Source Tracking

## Overview

Media source tracking enables linking facts to their original source media (videos, slides).

## Database Changes

Added to `fact_usage` table:
- `source_media_id` - Slide ID within story
- `source_media_url` - Actual video URL
- `source_media_type` - 'image' | 'video'
- `display_order` - Order within track
- `media_transcript_id` - Link to transcript

## Benefits

1. Track which video generated which facts
2. Enable fact reuse across tracks
3. Support cleanup when slides deleted
4. Enable media library features
